@startuml
actor SalesClerk

participant ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI
participant ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredController
participant ChangeAllToBeingDeliveredService
participant OrderRepository
participant ChangeToBeingDeliveredService

SalesClerk -> SalesClerk : 1 Update the status of dispatched orders to "Being delivered" for customer delivery.

SalesClerk -> ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI : 2 orderDispatched()
ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI -> ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredController : 3 orderDispatched()
ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredController -> ChangeAllToBeingDeliveredService : 4 orderDispatched()

ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredController --> ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI : 5 ordersDispatched

ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI --> SalesClerk : 6 Shows all the orders that are dispatched.
ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI --> SalesClerk : 7 Asks to choose one of the orders
SalesClerk -> ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI : 8 Selects the order he wants to change status

ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI -> ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredController : 9 changeToBeingDelivered(order)
ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredController -> ChangeToBeingDeliveredService : 10 changeToBeingDelivered(order)
ChangeToBeingDeliveredService -> OrderRepository : 11 changeToBeingDelivered(order)

ChangeToBeingDeliveredService --> ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI : 12 Successful change
ChangeOrderToBeingDeliveredUI --> SalesClerk : 13 Informs that is changed

@enduml